---
title: American Lamb Mince Chilli Nachos with Corn Chips & Tomato Salsa
description: We’re doing nachos like no other because they’re veggie-fied with a saucy and spiced lamb mince that will have your mouth watering. You can go all out with the toppings too, like a creamy mayo or tomato salsa.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
